      ..art >
        (factorial 6)   ------.
        (fact-iter   1 1 6)   |
        (fact-iter   1 2 6)   |
        (fact-iter   2 3 6)   |
        (fact-iter   6 4 6)   |
        (fact-iter  24 5 6)   |
        (fact-iter 120 6 6)   |
