#         < src..
        ..src > scheme
          (newtons-method (cubic a b c) 1)
        < src..

#         to approximate zeros of the cubic @m(x³ + ax² + bx + c).
        Para aproximar ceros de la cúbica @m(x³ + ax² + bx + c).

