#         ──────────────┤ make-rat  numer  denom ├──────────────
#                       ╰────────────────────────╯
#                       Rational numbers as pairs
#                           ╭────────────────╮
#         ──────────────────┤ cons  car  cdr ├──────────────────
#                           ╰────────────────╯
#                     However pairs are implemented
#       < art..
      ..art >
